videos.description: North Carolina's Kenny Williams and Joel Berry II knock down 3s on back-to-back possessions against Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Back-to-back 3s put UNC up early

videos.description: Head coach Mike Brey says he likes Notre Dame's tempo and the way they are playing at the half down 4 to North Carolina.
videos.headline: Brey: 'We're right where we want to be'

videos.description: North Carolina's Luke Maye takes the inside pass from Cameron Johnson and hits a layup on the Tar Heels' first possession of the half.
videos.headline: Maye opens 2nd half with quick score

videos.description: Joel Berry II drives in the lane and sinks a floater while drawing a foul to set up a 3-point play for North Carolina.
videos.headline: Berry falls and scores while drawing foul

videos.description: John Mooney sinks his sixth 3-pointer of the game for the Fighting Irish.
videos.headline: Mooney stays perfect from deep for Notre Dame

videos.description: North Carolina's Cameron Johnson drives baseline and throws down a slam then Notre Dame's Martinas Geben gets a dunk of his own on the ensuing Fighting Irish possession.
videos.headline: Johnson, Geben exchange jams
